/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The vantage point is high, providing a bird's eye view of the urban landscape. The street, teeming with life, stretches out below, flanked by towering buildings and lush green trees. Cars and buses traverse the road, adding a dynamic element to the scene. In the distance, a bridge arches over the street, connecting two parts of the city. The sky above is a clear blue, dotted with a few clouds, casting a serene backdrop to the busy street below.
